=You are a deduplication expert. Given a new pattern and a list of existing patterns, find if any existing one is semantically similar (>80% match in description, hook_type, emotions, triggers). Return the most similar pattern's ID (post_id) if match, else null.

:{{ $json.prompt_summary }}


Output JSON:
{
  "action": "update" or "create",
  "matching_id": "existing post_id if update, else null",
  "similarity_score": 0-100
}

